@EventService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5049

### Get one event by id — copy a real id from a search response below,
### since seeded ids are randomly generated fresh every time the DB is empty.
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/0935a2b8-26c3-4f8d-a554-d5fa206d4d50
Accept: application/json

### Not found — valid guid shape, but no such event
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

### Search — no filters, first page
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/search
Accept: application/json

### Search — keyword match (case-insensitive, matches "The Eras Tour")
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/search?keyword=eras
Accept: application/json

### Search — keyword with no matches
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/search?keyword=nomatch
Accept: application/json

### Search — date range
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/search?start=2026-08-01&end=2026-10-01
Accept: application/json

### Search — pagination (2 per page, second page)
GET {{EventService_HostAddress}}/events/search?pageSize=2&page=2
Accept: application/json

###
